Class StarterKitPageFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • page.classes.StarterKitPageFactory

  • public class StarterKitPageFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    public class StarterKitPageFactory
    Author:
    John Steele Description This class defines the web elements that a user would interact with in configuring their Starter Kit. Methods are provided for selecting 3 random nail wraps and a random name for their personal Jamberry website.
